# Project Context: acorbat.github.io

## Project Overview
Personal portfolio and professional webpage for **Agustin Corbat**, a Senior Image and Data Analyst with a PhD in Physics and expertise in bioimage analysis. The site serves as a comprehensive record of professional work, research projects, CV, and contact information.

## Project Purpose
- Showcase professional portfolio and completed projects
- Display expertise in image analysis, biophysics, and deep learning
- Provide CV/resume information
- Enable contact and professional networking
- Archive project details, research collaborations, and technical work

## Professional Profile
- **Title**: Senior Image and Data Analyst, Physicist, BioImage Analyst
- **Expertise**: Image analysis, deep learning, physics-based modeling, bioimage analysis, scientific computing
- **Background**: PhD Physicist with practical knowledge from a core medicine career
- **Focus**: Turning complex visual data from any source into clear, measurable results

