## Technology Stack
- **Framework**: Bootstrap 5.3.1 (responsive HTML/CSS framework)
- **Template Base**: iPortfolio (BootstrapMade.com template)
- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- **Libraries**: 
  - Typed.js for hero section animations
  - GLightbox for image galleries
  - Swiper for carousels
  - AOS for scroll animations
  - Isotope for portfolio filtering
  - Waypoints for scroll triggers
- **Backend**: PHP (contact form)
- **Hosting**: GitHub Pages

## Key Features
1. Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop
2. Smooth scrolling navigation
3. Animated hero section with typed text describing roles
4. Portfolio grid with project filtering
5. Services section describing professional offerings
6. Resume/CV section
